  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effect of medical humanities on medical student bias and clinical management is unclear.
      This study characterized medical student attitudes toward obese individuals and whether
      reading a play employing empathic characters can modulate negative reactions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
